name: Levelo Apps
blurb: Fun and simple to pick up and play apps and games by Levelo for PC and mobile devices!

rewards.reward: Pawn Class - Thank you for supporting our games and apps, every bit helps! You will receive two exclusive full HD wallpapers. One of the Levelo brand and another of an upcoming game being developed by Levelo, Breakout Hero. You will also have access to exclusive updates from us on our Kickstarter page as well as participation rights in any polls used for feedback.

Rook Class - Along with all previous rewards including the two exclusive full HD wallpapers, you will receive a digital download of the Wiggly Orange Fortune App. The app will be available for mobile devices and PC. You will receive it for PC, as mobile development requires initial funding.

Knight Class - You will receive the 2 exclusive full HD wallpapers, a digital copy of the Wiggly Fortune App, and a digital copy of the Slime Assault App! All apps will be available for mobile devices and PC. You will receive them for PC, as mobile development requires initial funding.

Bishop Class - You will receive the 2 exclusive full HD wallpapers,  a digital copy of the Wiggly Fortune App, and YOUR choice of ONE of the following apps in digital format: Slime Assault, Spaceship Crash Course, or Tank Attack. All apps will be available for mobile devices and PC. You will receive them for PC, as mobile development requires initial funding.

Queen Class - You will receive the 2 exclusive full HD wallpapers, a digital copy of the Wiggly Fortune App, and ALL of the following apps in digital format: Slime Assault, Spaceship Crash Course, and Tank Attack. All apps will be available for mobile devices and PC. You will receive them for PC, as mobile development requires initial funding.

King Class - You will receive all rewards from the Queen Class; the 2 exclusive full HD wallpapers,  a digital copy of the Wiggly Fortune App, and ALL of the following apps in digital format: Slime Assault, Spaceship Crash Course, and Tank Attack. All apps will be available for mobile devices and PC. You will receive them for PC, as mobile development requires initial funding.

AND

You will get the Breakout Hero Game for PC bundled with everything above!

Demi God - You will receive all the rewards from the King Class and a Developer's Diary video. Your name will forever be enshrined in digital format...your name will appear in the credits of the game, Breakout Hero under the Demi God section.

God - You will receive all the rewards from the King Class and a Developer's Diary video. Your name will forever be enshrined in digital format...your name will appear in the credits of the game, Breakout Hero under the God section.\r\nYou will also receive my greatest reward, my eternal gratitude.
